Package: nixtlaR
Title: R SDK For TimeGPT
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mariana", "Menchero", , "mariana@nixtla.oi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An SDK to interface with Nixtla's TimeGPT from R. 
    It provides functions for setting and validating tokens, and for generating forecasts with TimeGPT via API calls.
    Compatible with the tsibble package and base R. 
License: Apache License (>= 2.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    httr2,
    tsibble
Suggests: 
    httptest2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://mmenchero.github.io/nixtlaR/
